{# check_resources.j2 - Resource Availability Check Step #}
{# This template documents the resource check step. The actual query is performed #}
{# by the ResourceAvailabilityChecker which queries the SQL database. #}

Step: Check Resource Availability
Description: Query internal database for available experts and reallocatable resources.

Input: Project requirements extracted from user input

This step will:
1. Extract likely required skills from the project description
2. Query the employees table for available experts matching those skills
3. Check project assignments for resources on lower priority projects
4. Calculate skill coverage and make recommendations

The results will be available in the pipeline state as `check_resources`.
